inaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/03\/30\/consume-usury-humiliation\/","url_meta":{"origin":38092,"position":0},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Usury: Those who consume usury will be humiliated","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 30, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Tabari reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIt will be said on the Day of Resurrection to those who consumed usury: Take your weapon for war!\u201d Then he recited the verse, \u201cThose who consume usury cannot stand but as one stands who is being beaten by\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/03\/riba-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":38092,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Allah curses all involved in usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has cursed the one who consumes usury, its client, its witness, and its recorder. Usury and adultery do not become widespread among people but that they will become vulnerable to the punishment of Allah Almighty.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11996,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/03\/punishment-zina-riba\/","url_meta":{"origin":38092,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Warning: Adultery and usury widespread, punishment follows","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAdultery and usury do not become prevalent among people but that the punishment of Allah Almighty is justified against them.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 4502 Grade:\u00a0Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32398,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/21\/worst-act-of-usury-backbite\/","url_meta":{"origin":38092,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Worst act of usury to backbite, slander a believer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Zayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the worst act of usury is to attack the reputation of a Muslim without a just cause.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4876 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32396,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/21\/seventy-two-doors-riba\/","url_meta":{"origin":38092,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Seventy-two doors of usury include backbiting, slander","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cUsury has seventy-two doors, the least of which is like a man who goes into his mother. The worst act of usury is for a man to attack the reputation of his brother.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29444,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/14\/bribery-great-door-of-riba\/","url_meta":{"origin":38092,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Bribery: Accepting a bribe is a great door of usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever intercedes for his brother and he is given a gift for it and he accepts it, he has come to a great door among the doors of usury.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3541 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/38092","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{